--!nocheck
--[[
	Instance → Lua Converter v3
	Converts any Roblox instance hierarchy into executable Lua code.
	Supports every serialisable property type in the Roblox engine.
	
	Usage:
	  1. Change ObjectToConvert below to any instance path.
	  2. Run the game (or F5 in Studio).
	  3. The output appears in the scrollable TextBox.
	  4. Click "Copy" to copy to clipboard.
]]

